      "writtenOn": "2026-04-28T16:47:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The intent behind this return type is to distinguish between two cases:\n\n1. No redundant EEPROM path defined → not treated as a failure, but a “not applicable” case.\n\n2. Redundant path exists → return the VPD collection result (bool(success/failure) + path)",
