      "message": "I have left a comment on the subsequent commit regarding limitation of this return type in case of multiple failure paths.\n\n\nNow for that you will have to pass error code and set them differently. Instead I would suggest go for simple solution where one API does one thing so that return types need not be overloaded.\n\nWe already have API to get redundant path for a given EEPROM path, use that. \"getRedundantEepromPathFromJson\"",
